def find_intersection(set1, set2):
    """
    Return a new set with elements present in both set1 and
    set2.
    """
    intersection_set = set()
    smaller_set = min(set1, set2)
    bigger_set = set2 if smaller_set == set1 else set1
    for element in smaller_set:
        if element in bigger_set:
            intersection_set.add(element)

    return intersection_set

def find_intersection(set1, set2):
    lists=[]
    set4=list(set1)
    set5=list(set2)
    for i in set1:
        if i in set2:
            lists.append(i)
            set4.remove(i)
            set5.remove(i)
    set3=set(lists)
    return set3
